    ],
    "external_research_note": "Routing controlled by ANALYST_GEMINI_DEEP_RESEARCH_ENABLED on the analyst host. Gemini credentials live with the analyst service; platform never calls Gemini directly. See docs/ANALYST_GEMINI_DEPLOYMENT.md.",
